Invocation Name: top searches
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Guess the position of a top Google search, and Alexa will tell you if you need to guess higher or lower in this fun, learning game!

Learn more about how people across the world are using Google to search up things and discover surprising popular searches

She will also tell you how many times you have played.

Stop anytime by saying "Alexa, stop"

All data from:
https://trends.google.com/trends/yis/2019/GLOBAL/
